Description_lang: An exceptional spell that heals an ally for $m1% of their maximum health, ignoring healing reduction effects.

description_blz.en_US: An exceptional spell that heals an ally for 40% of their maximum health, ignoring healing reduction effects.

description_blz.ko_KR: 뛰어난 주문을 시전하여 아군을 최대 생명력의 40%만큼 치유합니다. 치유량 감소 효과를 무시합니다.
description_blz.zh_TW: 強效法術，能夠使一個盟友恢復相當於其生命力上限40%的生命力，且無視降低治療的效果。
